name: Flexport
tag_list: customs-broker, logistics, international-trade, import-export, global-trade, globalization, customs-brokerage, international-shipping
overview:
Flexport simplifies the import-export process for small businesses.

As the first licensed US customs brokerage with a beautiful web application for managing your international shipping, we will make global trade easier, more affordable and more predictable for our customers.

Our goal is to fulfill the Web’s promise of empowering every person on the planet to trade seamlessly with each other without regard to geographic, cultural or political boundaries. By tackling complicated regulatory and logistics matters in the background as if by magic, Flexport will make international trade simpler than at any time in the history of humanity.

In a multi-trillion dollar global logistics industry known for greeting small businesses with confusion, red tape, and price discrimination, Flexport is addressing a huge underserved market segment where legacy logistics companies will find it uneconomical to compete.
